Abstract: MACTAS-Celia. Age 89. Survived by her loving children Arline, David (Ellen) and Leonard (Leah), brother Jack Swidler, adoring grandchildren and cherished great-grandchildren. Services are Sunday, 10 A.M., at Robert Schoem's Menorah Chapel, 150 Route 4 East, Paramus, NJ.
